<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Перезапуск бота | Resistance</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/logo.jpg">
    <style>
    :root {
            --bg-color: #f5f7fa;
            --text-color: #333;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --header-bg: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            --border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            --primary: #4a3aff;
            --primary-hover: #3728e0;
            --nav-link-color: #333;
            --nav-link-hover: #4a3aff;
            --footer-color: #999;
            --gradient-1: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            --gradient-2: linear-gradient(45deg, #6343d4, #aa4eff);
            --shadow-sm: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            --shadow-md: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            --shadow-lg: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] {
            --bg-color: #0b0c1e;
            --text-color: #e0e0e0;
            --card-bg: #1a1b2f;
            --header-bg: rgba(10,10,20,0.95);
            --border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            --primary: #aa4eff;
            --primary-hover: #8a3fcc;
            --nav-link-color: #e0e0e0;
            --nav-link-hover: #aa4eff;
            --footer-color: #666;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Шапка (аналогично другим страницам) */
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            background: var(--header-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .logo img {
            height: 50px;
            width: auto;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(170, 78, 255, 0.5));
        }

        .logo h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            background: var(--gradient-2);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .user-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .user-info span {
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .btn-logout {
            padding: 8px 20px;
            background: var(--gradient-2);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-logout:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(170,78,255,0.4);
        }

        .theme-toggle {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: background 0.3s;
            color: var(--text-color);
        }

        .theme-toggle:hover {
            background: rgba(128,128,128,0.2);
        }

        .theme-toggle .sun,
        .theme-toggle .moon {
            transition: transform 0.5s, opacity 0.3s;
        }

        [data-theme="light"] .theme-toggle .moon {
            display: none;
        }
        [data-theme="dark"] .theme-toggle .sun {
            display: none;
        }

        /* Контейнер */
        .container {
            max-width: 1300px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        /* Заголовок */
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            background: var(--gradient-2);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        /* Карточки статистики */
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 30px 25px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .stat-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 5px;
            background: var(--gradient-2);
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
        }

        .stat-icon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: var(--gradient-2);
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .stat-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--footer-color);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        /* Раздел действий */
        .actions-section {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 40px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .actions-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: var(--text-color);
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary);
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .action-buttons {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .action-btn {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            background: rgba(170,78,255,0.1);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 30px;
            color: var(--text-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .action-btn svg {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            fill: var(--primary);
        }

        .action-btn:hover {
            background: var(--gradient-2);
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        .action-btn:hover svg {
            fill: white;
        }

        .action-btn.danger {
            background: rgba(255,71,87,0.1);
            color: #ff4757;
        }

        .action-btn.danger svg {
            fill: #ff4757;
        }

        .action-btn.danger:hover {
            background: #ff4757;
            color: white;
        }

        .action-btn.danger:hover svg {
            fill: white;
        }

        /* График (заглушка для красоты) */
        .chart-container {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 40px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .chart-container h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--text-color);
        }

        .chart-placeholder {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-end;
            justify-content: space-around;
            height: 200px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .bar {
            flex: 1;
            background: var(--gradient-2);
            border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;
            transition: height 0.3s;
            position: relative;
            min-width: 30px;
        }

        .bar:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .bar-label {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: var(--footer-color);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Футер */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            color: var(--footer-color);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        /* Адаптивность */
        @media (max-width: 700px) {
            .header {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            .stats-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">...</header>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Перезапуск бота</h1>
        <div style="background: var(--card-bg); border-radius: 30px; padding: 40px; text-align: center;">
            <span style="font-size: 4rem;">🤖</span>
            <h2 style="margin: 20px 0;">Вы уверены, что хотите перезапустить бота?</h2>
            <p>Это действие отключит бота на несколько секунд.</p>
            <form action="/admin/bot/restart" method="POST" style="margin-top: 30px;">
                <button type="submit" class="btn-logout" style="background: #ff4757;">Да, перезапустить</button>
                <a href="/admin/dashboard" class="btn-logout" style="background: #666; margin-left: 15px;">Отмена</a>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">...</footer>
</body>
</html>